              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "# The body's acute stress response"
              },
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Our bodies are equipped with a super-efficient defense system: stress. When we experience something threatening, the brain quickly starts focusing on fighting or fleeing."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "I want to know more",
                "sectionId": "section2"
              },
              {
                "component": "NextConversationButton",
                "variant": "primary",
                "content": "Skip",
                "conversationId": "kroppen-3"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "id": "section1",
        "alias": "section1",
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Our heart may beat faster, we may sweat, tense our muscles, get tunnel vision or breathe faster than usual."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "continue",
                "sectionId": "section3"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "id": "section2",
        "alias": "section2",
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "It is a natural reaction to stress, and helped our ancestors survive in situations where it was important to quickly get away from a tiger or fight back against a rivaling tribe."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "continue",
                "sectionId": "section4"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "id": "section3",
        "alias": "section3",
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
      {
        "content": [
          {
            "component": "TextGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "We still react the same way, but the threats we face today are a little different: getting tasks done on time or handling a difficult comment online."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
              {
                "component": "Button",
                "content": "continue",
                "sectionId": "section5"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "id": "section4",
        "alias": "section4",
        "type": "defaultSection"
      },
